kpi_info.use: Number of usage of G.711 a-law codec with 30ms packetization period with CN codec on Nb(SIP-I) and MB interfaces.Updated:When Nb(SIP-I) or Mb termination is completely reserved successfully with G.711(a-law) codec and 30 ms packetization period is used with CN codec.

kpi_info.title: CODEC_G711_U_30_CN (M643C156)
kpi_info.use: Number of usage of G.711 u-law codec with 30ms packetization period with CN codec on Nb(SIP-I) and MB interfaces.Updated:When Nb(SIP-I) or Mb termination is completely reserved successfully with G.711(u-law) codec and 30 ms packetization period is used wit CN codec.

kpi_info.title: CODEC_FR_AMR_WB_ERROR (M643C157)
kpi_info.use: Number of unsuccessful activation attempts of FR AMR-WB codec in the Ater interface.Updated:When DSP informs the MGW bearer control that use of FR AMR-WB codec in the Ater interface does not succeed.

kpi_info.title: SPEECH_TO_CLEARMODE_AOIP (M643C158)
kpi_info.use: Cumulative number of successful codec modifications from any speech codec to Clearmode in AoIP interface.Updated:When codec reservation from DSP is successful for asked codec modification.

kpi_info.title: CLEARMODE_TO_SPEECH_AOIP (M643C159)
kpi_info.use: Cumulative number of successful codec modifications from Clearmode to any speech codec in AoIP interface.Updated:When codec reservation from DSP is successful for asked codec modification.

kpi_info.title: A_U_LAW_CONVERSION (M643C160)
kpi_info.use: Cumulative number of successful G.711 codec conversion from A-law to μ-law, or vice versa.Updated:When termination is completely reserved successfully with G.711 (a- or u-law) codec and there is transcoding from a-law to u-law, or vice versa.

kpi_info.title: A_U_LAW_CONVERSION_ERROR (M643C161)
kpi_info.use: Number of unsuccessful G.711 conversion from A-law to u-law, or vice versa.Updated:When termination is completely reserved successfully with G.711(a- or u-law) codec and there is transcoding from a-law to u-law, or vice versa. However, transcoding is rejected for any reason.

kpi_info.title: WB_TRANSCODER_CAT2 (M643C162)
kpi_info.use: Number of transcoder category 2 used. Transcoder category 2 includes transcoding between internal wideband codec and codec category 2.Updated:When reserving or modifying transcoding resources from transcoder category 2 is successful.

kpi_info.title: WB_TRANSCODER_CAT2_ERROR (M643C163)
kpi_info.use: Number of unsuccessful activation attempts of transcoder category 2. Transcoder category 2 includes transcoding between internal wideband codec and codec category 2.Updated:When reserving or modifying transcoding resources from transcoder category 2 is unsuccessful.
